                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/3028" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">EPSM-0234</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9281 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">做好看的音乐——大河宝玉：21世纪的大学生创业故事</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Making Music Beautiful - DaHeBaoYu(DHBY): A College Students&#39; Entrepreneurship Story in 21st Century</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">刘国亮，张汇川</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">吉林大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">长春市大河宝玉文化传媒有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">文化、体育和娱乐业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人力资源部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大学生创业；公司实体化；虚拟化运营；互联交流；自媒体</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">college student’s entrepreneurship, corporate materialization, virtualization operations, internet communication, self-media </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例描述了长春市大河宝玉文化传媒有限公司的创建和早期发展历程。从创建之日起，大河宝玉就将自己定位为一家专注于校园MV拍摄的低消费服务型企业。大河宝玉在由虚拟转换为现实的过程中经历了许多挫折与困难，同时也让整个公司都获得了成长，而后根据发展的需要，公司又重新将现实转化为虚拟。灵活的公司形态和顺应时代的决策，保证了大河宝玉作为一个实力较弱的大学生企业在汹涌澎湃、大浪淘沙的社会洪流中生存了下来。在大河宝玉在不断面对挑战、战胜困难挫折的同时，也在不断学习和调整。在经过团队建设、产品优化、拓展业务、发现新市场等一系列改进之后，大河宝玉终于等到了大学生创业的时代高潮，并收获了相应的成功果实。然而，随着“互联网+”时代的到来和人人自媒体的新移动终端的普及，危机再次来临，大河宝玉若想继续在时代的洪流中生存下去，必须面对新一轮的挑战，并且克服困难，寻求新的康庄大道。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case describes the creation and early development of Changchun DHBY Culture Media Co. DHBY point itself as a low-cost service-oriented enterprises which focus on the campus MV shooting at the very first time. DHBY has experienced many setbacks and difficulties in the process of virtual conversion to reality, while those difficulties also making the whole company grow up, and then seeking for more development opportunity, the company has re-transformed the reality into virtual again. Flexible corporate form and right decisions which suit to time, to ensure that the DHBY survived as a weak company which is a student’s entrepreneurship. While DHBY faces challenges, it never stops learning and adjusting itself to overcome difficulties setbacks. After a series of improvements, such as team building, product optimization, business development and discovery of new markets, DHBY finally met the peak of college students&#39; entrepreneurship and harvested the fruits of success. However, the crisis came again with the &quot;Internet +&quot; era and the popularity of the new digital media, DHBY must face a new round of challenges and overcome difficulties to seek a new broad road if DHBY want to continue to survive under the crisp society.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2016</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业战略管理》、《创业管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">低成本创业</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2017-11</td>
                            </tr>
